@startuml
title Testing Pyramid and Fullstack Architecture

skinparam shadowing false

rectangle "build.py / ctest" as Build

package "Fast feedback" {
  [Server Unit Tests]
  [Repository Integration Tests]
  [HTTP Contract Tests]
  [Qt Model/View Tests]
}

package "System confidence" {
  [GUI Startup Smoke]
  [Qt Live Fullstack Tests]
  [Package / Migration Smokes]
}

rectangle "FullstackServerHarness\n(QProcess + temp DB + live HTTP)" as Harness
rectangle "Qt Test / QTest / QSignalSpy" as QtTest

Build --> [Server Unit Tests]
Build --> [Repository Integration Tests]
Build --> [HTTP Contract Tests]
Build --> [Qt Model/View Tests]
Build --> [GUI Startup Smoke]
Build --> [Qt Live Fullstack Tests]
Build --> [Package / Migration Smokes]

QtTest --> [Qt Model/View Tests]
QtTest --> [Qt Live Fullstack Tests]
Harness --> [Qt Live Fullstack Tests]

note right of [Qt Live Fullstack Tests]
Implemented this turn:
- main workspace loading against live server
- invoice export verification against live server
end note
@enduml
